OL,4,CMan told he is not British after 42
OL,5,Cyears in UK
OL,6,GA retired 74-year-old Ghanaian man who
OL,7,Ghas lived in the UK for nearly 50
OL,8,Gyears must wait a decade before the
OL,9,GHome Office will let him stay
OL,10,Gpermanently.
OL,12,FNelson Shardey, from Wallasey in
OL,13,FWirral, had for many years assumed he
OL,14,Fwas officially seen as British.
OL,16,FHe only discovered otherwise in 2019
OL,17,Fand, despite paying taxes all his
OL,18,Fadult life, now faces paying thousands
OL,19,Fof pounds to stay and use the NHS.
OL,21,FThe Home Office declined to comment on
OL,22,Fthe ongoing legal case.
